data.description: Welcome home! This lovely 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence and a large enclosed Florida Room offers the perfect blend of function, comfort, and privacy. It was a model home for the builder! Nestled on a private home site in the much sought after community of Marion Landing, this property provides a serene escape while being walking distance from wonderful amenities like a Clubhouse, fitness center, tennis/pickleball courts, library and even a 8 lane bowling alley among many others. Roof was redone in 2008, A/C in 2012 and a newer water heater. A new garage door was just installed. This home was freshly repainted on the inside and features tile floors throughout the home for easy upkeep. The bright kitchen has lots of counter and cabinet space along with an eating area overlooking a bay window. The large living room has a wood burning fireplace bordered with double sliders going out into the enclosed Florida room which is under heat and air. Enjoy the beauty of the outdoors year-round while staying protected from the elements. There is also an indoor utility room with a door going out to the beautiful backyard. Wait till you see how private the backyard is! Whether you envision relaxing evenings under the stars or hosting barbecues with loved ones, this outdoor space provides the ideal backdrop for making cherished memories. Come see this home before it is SOLD!
